  "title": "🎆 Marketing & Events — New Year, New Career 🎆",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview / Employee Value Proposition</strong></p><p>EMINENCE ORGANIZATION is a dynamic events and sales company that thrives on creativity and energy. Our young and vibrant team brings fresh ideas to the table, ensuring every project is as bold and exciting as the next. Here, we don’t just market products or drive sales—we create moments that stick.</p><p>Let’s make magic happen!</p><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>Kick off the New Year with a role that builds confidence, communication, and career momentum. Join our Marketing & Events team to work on live campaigns, roadshows, and brand activations while learning valuable marketing and people skills. No experience required — full training provided.🚀</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Support and execute marketing and event campaigns to increase brand awareness and customer engagement</li><li>Represent brands at events and promotional activities to create memorable and positive customer interactions</li><li>Engage customers directly to deliver positive brand experiences and encourage participation</li><li>Collaborate with mentors to develop marketing, communication, and event management skills through hands-on learning</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Motivation to learn and adapt in a fast-paced, people-oriented environment</li><li>Openness to stepping out of comfort zones to grow professionally</li><li>Suitable for fresh graduates and career switchers seeking growth opportunities</li></ul>",
